title: 2017 Ranked Rewards Help Desk
body:
Hello friends!

We've created a nifty [compendium for 2017 Ranked Rewards](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/player-support/W0aEONuP-2017-ranked-rewards-help-desk), bundled with a fancy countdown.  Check it out for all of your questions and discussion!
